Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,攔阻網陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,9號10號發射管 侵蝕魚雷 發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,400
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 400
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…要道歉
